Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.29,0:00:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.62,0:00:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边的加工完了 你能检查一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.58,0:00:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.04,0:00:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.42,0:00:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快 好手艺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有问题的话请跟我说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…没有 完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡沏好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是用我从店里带过来的用具沏的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道很正的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮大忙了 沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尾张小姐不介意的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椰子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.90,0:00:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让金属史莱姆成我们的伙伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.78,0:00:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.70,0:00:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店长 期限是到星期天的几点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 考虑到坐电车要花的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.12,0:00:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上九点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.76,0:00:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 金属史莱姆逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:00:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 别玩了给我去泡咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.85,0:01:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后天 星期天 审查会!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.94,0:01:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.73,0:01:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.45,0:01:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦 毕竟是黑咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.55,0:01:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.05,0:01:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《旋转吧!》九 着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.44,0:01:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟那么努力了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.78,0:01:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真的很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:01:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了 太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椰子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椰子!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡…睡死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店长 要迟到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一站是 秦 秦 换乘南叶线的乘客请准备下车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漫画巡回审查会场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这儿的书店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开始紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1600.62,318.233)}少年Monday\N漫画巡回审查会场\N在这前面右转就到了哦!\N受理5:00结束\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,审查会上会有专业编辑来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我不管来几次都不习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是咖啡店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天…不对 是今天多亏了你们俩帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啦 我只不过是泡了点咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老哥是真的什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说傻话了 我昨天可是通了四款游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才说你只是在玩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适当的杂音更能让人集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杂…音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 到底怎么样了呢 椰子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我都紧张起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.06,0:05:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙今天一整天都在说这事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有…有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定椰子都要成为漫画家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是觉得冷静不下来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 等他回来要不要开个庆祝会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太心急了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该先开犒劳会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我觉得今夭还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的超紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿田九先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿田…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:05:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问…这是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:06:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概会很失落得回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个水平完全可以开始连载了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 拿新人奖也不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由原作者九老师所描绘的漫画《旋转吧!》
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1675.956,149.136)}{\fs45}创下了记录的空前大热潮\N探究现在成为话题的漫画\N《旋转吧!》高人气的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為了破紀録的大熱作品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是由少年Monday连载
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在女性中也人气很高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,获得今年的日本漫画新人大奖的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是九老师的"旋转吧!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些 你用了多久画完的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:07:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然开始画是三个月之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际画的时间大概只有两三周
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两周左右？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…是的 实际上两周左右
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画得还挺快的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不算说慌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能多花点时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本想一页一页修改
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是后面还有人 我就尽量总结一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没注意到时间是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该没什么集中力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对擅长的地方很自信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不擅长的地方却不敢正视
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能有效地利用时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面能看出你的藉囗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概真正集中用功的时间也就这两天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然 你为了今天能画出来我是觉得很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:07:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬要说有点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是年轻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五分钟就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我花了三小时过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,审查我的漫画就用了五分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中力？借口？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借口是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为店里的事很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想办法搞定的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想办法…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么在当店长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 不好意思 好像说了奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 我才是太兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的担心要是多余的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才由于降雪原因 一部分的列车停运或延误
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有停运的列车还未确定什么时间恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电车什么时候开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是停运真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去后无法面对一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有沙耶和豆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还特地来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是不适合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是九嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么 在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好久不见 萤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见 九
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了和欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了 椰子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:21.03,opcn,,0,0,0,,My honey
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:23.05,opcn,,0,0,0,,甜蜜的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.03,opcn,,0,0,0,,若是咬下一口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:26.01,opcn,,0,0,0,,甜蜜的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.13,0:02:27.08,opcn,,0,0,0,,激动之心就会渐渐满溢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:30.12,opcn,,0,0,0,,噼里啪啦火花四溅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:34.70,opcn,,0,0,0,,在身体各处爆发开来
